---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/sections/Hero.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/sections/CtaBand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Meet the certified interpretive guide behind OutMore Adventures. Two decades of Yosemite knowledge, one transformative experience."
>
  <Hero
    headline="About OutMore Adventures"
    subheadline="Born from 20 years of falling in love with the same place, over and over again."
    fullHeight={false}
    backgroundImage="/images/heroes/bridalveil-fall.jpg"
  />

  <!-- Founder Story -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-valley-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Photo Placeholder -->
        <div class="w-full md:w-80 aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl bg-granite-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <div class="text-center text-granite-mid p-8">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-sm">Founder photo coming soon</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story -->
        <div class="prose-lg">
          <h2 class="mb-6">The Story Behind OutMore</h2>
          <p class="text-granite-mid text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Over twenty years ago, I came to Yosemite for what I thought would be a season. Two decades later,
            I'm still here — and the park still surprises me every single day.
          </p>
          <p class="text-granite-mid text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In that time, I've had the privilege of interpreting Yosemite for thousands of visitors — sharing
            the geology that tells a story three billion years in the making, the ecology that sustains one of
            the most remarkable ecosystems on Earth, and the human history that stretches back thousands of years
            before this land became a national park.
          </p>
          <p class="text-granite-mid text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            I've watched the seasons cycle through the Valley more times than I can count. I've seen waterfalls
            that roar like thunder in spring and granite faces that glow at sunset in ways that stop me in my
            tracks — even now, even after all these years. I've tracked wildlife, studied the forest, learned
            from Indigenous knowledge keepers, and walked every trail in conditions that range from wildflower
            carpets to waist-deep snow.
          </p>
          <p class="text-granite-mid text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            OutMore Adventures was born from a simple realization: most people who visit Yosemite only scratch
            the surface. They see the big views, take the photos, and leave. But Yosemite is so much deeper than
            that. The stories written in the granite, the relationships between species, the cultural significance
            that predates the park by millennia — these are the things that transform a visit into an experience.
          </p>
          <p class="text-granite-dark text-lg leading-relaxed font-semibold">
            I started OutMore because I want you to see Yosemite the way I do — not as a tourist, but as someone
            who truly understands this place. That's what twenty years of living here can offer, and I'm ready to
            share it with you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-granite-mid text-lg mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We believe that interpretation transforms the way people connect with the natural world.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-sequoia/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sequoia" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Connection Over Consumption</h3>
          <p class="text-granite-mid leading-relaxed">
            We don't race through a checklist. We slow down, look closer, and help you build a real
            relationship with this landscape. Understanding breeds care.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-sequoia/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sequoia" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Depth Over Distance</h3>
          <p class="text-granite-mid leading-relaxed">
            We'd rather you understand one meadow deeply than photograph ten overlooks quickly. Real knowledge
            changes how you see — not just Yosemite, but the natural world everywhere.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-sequoia/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sequoia" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Stewardship Through Understanding</h3>
          <p class="text-granite-mid leading-relaxed">
            When people understand a place, they protect it. Every experience we lead is an investment in
            Yosemite's future — creating advocates for the park through education and connection.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credentials -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-granite-dark">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-white mb-12">Credentials & Experience</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-golden-grass mb-2">20+</p>
          <p class="text-granite-light text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Years in Yosemite</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-golden-grass mb-2">CIG</p>
          <p class="text-granite-light text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Certified Interpretive Guide</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-golden-grass mb-2">CUA</p>
          <p class="text-granite-light text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">NPS Commercial Use Authorization</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-golden-grass mb-2">NAI</p>
          <p class="text-granite-light text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Professional Member</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-granite-light text-center mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        OutMore Adventures is one of a limited number of operators holding a Commercial Use Authorization
        directly from the National Park Service to conduct guided experiences in Yosemite.
        This authorization means your experience meets the highest standards of safety, insurance, and stewardship.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="Experience Yosemite Through Our Eyes"
    subtext="Join us for a day that will transform how you see the park."
    ctaText="Learn About the Experience"
    ctaHref="/experience/"
    variant="sequoia"
  />
</BaseLayout>
